261
00:17:31,426 --> 00:17:34,656
Call me if you get something like that, okay?

262
00:17:34,656 --> 00:17:38,056
Seriously, what was he thinking?

263
00:17:38,056 --> 00:17:40,136
What was it? What was it about?

264
00:17:40,136 --> 00:17:43,756
Huh? You don't have to know.

265
00:17:43,756 --> 00:17:46,246
